sentences.english: With their help, all the apples were picked and put back on the cart.

sentences.english: This ship model is a miniature copy of a life-sized Arab dhow called the Sohar.
sentences.chinese: 这是名为“苏哈尔”的阿拉伯帆船模型。

sentences.english: The person who Bob and Sue caught in the park was very young.
sentences.chinese: 鲍伯和苏在公园里逮到的那个人很年轻。

sentences.english: The Sukhoi SU-22 is a robust and effective Soviet built ground attack aircraft.
sentences.chinese: 苏22是前苏联建造的一种威力强大的对地攻击战机。

sentences.english: I've been thinking of asking Sue, but then again, I thought I might ask Ann.
sentences.chinese: 我在想着邀请苏，但过一会儿我又觉得我该邀请安。

sentences.english: He kept the sixteen sous, and handed the five francs to the young girl.
sentences.chinese: 他留下了十六个苏，把五法郎给那姑娘。

sentences.english: Mother and Sue kissed Gretel goodbye.
sentences.chinese: 母亲和苏与格莱托亲吻道别。

sentences.english: By the way, did you call Sue?
sentences.chinese: 顺便一提，你打电话给苏了吗？

sentences.english: Sue wants a new skirt, but Jim wants a new bike.
sentences.chinese: 苏想要一条新裙子，吉姆想要一辆新自行车。

sentences.english: He also thanked the exhibition's organising committee headed by Mr John Man and Mrs Irene So.
sentences.chinese: 他并多谢画展的筹委会共同主席文锡辉及苏潘慕洁。

sentences.english: You see Sue sew Sue's new socks, sir.
sentences.chinese: 你看见苏缝苏的新袜子，先生。

sentences.english: Sue's face lighted up when she heard the good news.
sentences.chinese: 听到这个好消息时，苏流露出愉快的面容。

sentences.english: Histopathological examinations was performed using hematoxylin and eosin stain.
sentences.chinese: 组织病理学检查是用苏木质伊红染色。

sentences.english: The biggest obstacle toJapanese-Soviet relations remains the issue of the northern territories.
sentences.chinese: 日苏关系改善的最大障碍是领土问题。

sentences.english: Hey, Sue. Have you got any pain-killers at hand? I have a splitting headache.
sentences.chinese: 嗨，苏。你有止疼片吗？我头痛的快裂开了。
